WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:22.253
Darkness is trying to set in Mystery Babylon.

00:00:22.253 --> 00:00:37.320
I'm telling you, great Mystery Babylon.

00:00:37.320 --> 00:01:06.800
It will be like a dark blanket will blanket thee.

00:01:06.800 --> 00:01:41.267
If they choose this man (Zohran Mamdani), I see a dark blanket blanketing, and people will flee.

00:01:41.836 --> 00:01:55.849
I hear the word flee.

00:01:55.849 --> 00:02:27.120
They will leave by the tens of thousands, if not hundreds of thousands.

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:33.993
They will leave.

00:02:33.993 --> 00:02:56.154
People, I see them fleeing if he's voted in.

00:02:56.154 --> 00:03:12.625
People will know that this is the end.

00:03:12.625 --> 00:04:13.260
Father, you know if he'll be voted in or not; what I'm hearing you say is what I'm seeing is going to happen.

00:04:13.260 --> 00:04:33.865
He said, "No, they still have a choice.

00:04:33.865 --> 00:04:45.880
They have a choice to vote.

00:04:45.880 --> 00:04:55.009
" He's held a veil.

00:05:00.893 --> 00:05:34.687
I don't see the outcome, but I see the outcome if they vote this way concerning this man.

00:05:34.687 --> 00:06:09.400
I see a dark cloud; it's a dark blanket over them.

00:06:09.400 --> 00:06:27.250
And I see financial structures falling.

00:06:46.809 --> 00:06:56.590
I see the financial institutions and all the money falling.

00:07:04.537 --> 00:07:32.438
I see a fleeing of the city, like people saying, "We're out of here!

00:07:39.080 --> 00:08:04.720
" I see it's like a mass migration of people coming.

00:08:10.328 --> 00:08:17.400
People fleeing certain areas.
